akhil mishra is an indian film and television actor who has worked in films like hazaaron khwaishein aisi , mere dost picture abhi baki hai and television serials such as pradhanmantri . he is currently working in the serial do dil bandhe ek dori se . he became famous by doing the cameo role of librarian dubey in 3 idiots . he also acted in bhopal : a prayer for rain .